  <text>
    <body>
      <ab type="lido:objectWorkType">Leaflet</ab>
      <ab subtype="creation" type="lido:event">
        <date>1943 after</date>
      </ab>
      <ab type="lido:objectDescriptionSet">The frameless leaflet features sketched persons and objects. The background is black and green. In the centre of the image are a man and woman not looking at one another. He is dressed completely in white. To his right is a bottle with a white cross on it. The woman is dressed completely in black. In the lower part of the picture, the Serbo-Croatian film title is written in green and white Cyrillic letters: ‘Jača od smrti’ (Stronger than death). In the corner bottom right, the four letters ‘SBOP’ are printed.</ab>
      <ab subtype="comment" type="lido:objectDescriptionSet">‘Du gehörst zu mir’. Willy Birgel played the lead role of Prof. Dr. Burghardt. The film was directed by Gerhard Lamprecht and released in 1943. The four letters ‘SBOP’ are obviously the acronym of the (Serbian) film import company.</ab>
